721824f-a.title: Manhattan: Murray Street - Church Street
721824f-a.text:
Murray Street, north side, west from and including Church Sfreet, The view shows the Sixth Ave., Elevated bending at Church and Mutray Streets, to run west on Murray Street, for one block, to West Broadway,
vhere it turns again to run North and South.
May 26, 1904.
PETE228EE98e.
Neg, 2026

718872f-a.title: Manhattan: Church Street - Murray Street
718872f-a.text:
Church Street, south from Murray Street, showing mainly "El" demolition. At this point this structure swings to the right, to continue westward to West Broadway. The station stairs barely
discernible above the bus are at Park Place.
February 18, 1939
Dnift of W. A. Lucas
